                    <span>Every Christian should read this book instead of listening to the 628 right wing radio talk show personalities that make up the liberal media.(You like that one!) Two men named Jesus. Both claim to be the Messiah. Which one will we follow? Jesus said"Do unto others as others would do unto you". Not "Do unto others before they do you in." We need to follow the Jesus of love not power. Tony Campolo is a voice crying in the wilderness for our day.</span>
                  
              
